                h4 VISUAL HIERARCHY
                p
                    | I used 
                    span.highlight Z Pattern
                    | —Our eye starts scanning from top left to top right, then diagonally down to bottom left, stopping at the bottom right. For example, the reading flow of user profile starts with avatar and username. It is followed by content categories, and finally a list of specific items.
        .level.level--tropical-blue
